oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Parco Enterprises Job No. 37257
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1807) for an order placed for Parco Enterprises by X. B. Cosse for 7,000 one color tickets (3,500 for the 7 p.m. show and 3,500 for the 9:30 p.m.) for a performance by the Dick Clark Caravan of Stars at the Huntsville Coliseum on August 22. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
